rows.label: tlk70000047_03_msg0001
rows.name:
Watching your efforts has
really inspired me.

rows.label: tlk70000047_03_msg0002
rows.name:
I have always sought refuge
in my faith before. It feels fair
foolish now, though.

rows.label: tlk70000047_03_msg0003
rows.name:
I want to find something
real I can do for Freja.

rows.label: tlk70000047_03_msg0004
rows.name:
It's time to accept that Freja's
disease isn't going anywhere
unless I do something about it.

rows.label: tlk70000047_03_msg0005
rows.name:
I want to seek help for my poor girl.
But if it's not religion I put my faith in,
then I suppose all that's left is people.
